snippet.title: FROG - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Out Now! The first release from Pool Party Games! 

Play the game at: https://jamespoole.itch.io/frog

The online frog multiplayer experience that you have been waiting for from James Poole and Friends.

Find out more at:
https://twitter.com/itsapooleparty
https://www.instagram.com/james_gallagher_poole/

Trailer Directed by Graham Patterson

James Poole - Game Design, Development and Art
Pádraig Connolly - Backend Server and Game Development
Cathal Histon - Music, Audio and Creative Consulting Department
Graham Patterson - Voice Over and Creative Consulting Department
